Steps for preparing a new release

* Run unit tests
* Verify if tutorial and screenshots are up2date
* Set version info in Manifest
* update string help_whats_new and versionlist.html
* make sure that backdoors for monkeyrunner are commented out
* ant clean
* ant release
* test upgrade mechanism
* Create release tag in GIT
* cp APK and proguard folder into a new folder in releases
* upload to Android Market
* add recent changes in Market
* push gh-pages

